700488f-a.title: Bronx: Beach Avenue - Guerlain Avenue
700488f-a.text:
Beach Ave., east side,south from Guerlain Street to Archer Street,
showing newly erected buildings known as the Stratton Park Apartments.
The south side of Guerlain Street is seen extending east to Taylor Ave.
About 1929.
General Photographic Company.
